“Lost From Above” Finally Is Comingsoon. 

Collect moments of lust by the deep of jungle & atmosphere as the seasons change here at home East Java especially Tumpaksewu Waterfall the most energetic Falls i have ever seen.

Every time is mortal, nothing can be repeated except the recorded memory. Just remembering and reminiscing. 
There are only 2 choices in life, be good or be the best. Continue to improve and reflect on what your heart tells you.

Feel the freedom and intimacy with each other, give yourself a chance to be sensitive to every incident. What we breathe, what we see and what we hear is the perfect lesson for us to absorb, take the good and throw out the bad. Make everything easy and don't be hard to share

Shooting in ideal lighting isn’t always an option but with the new 20MP 4/3” CMOS sensor inside the Mavic 3 the possibilities are endless. With the much improved low light capabilities challenging lighting is challenging no more.

Made possible by the new Mavic 3 & it’s ability to go further & push the boundaries on what’s possible in challenging light conditions.

